            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Código <code>i &gt; 5</code> para que el bucle se ejecute cuando <code>i</code> sea mayor que <code>5</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i = \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i &gt; \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"; i--) {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(i);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"17\" endIndex=\"22\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"10\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"9\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"8\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"7\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"6\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>i &gt; 5</code>.</p></body></html>"
